page.title: 14Newquay Census
page.content:
It was decided to take a census to find out about people living in Newquay-what they do;how old they are; where they live;what sized families they have;what are their hopes and fears...
We sent out questionnaires to all the pupils in the first and second year classes,but some people answered only some of the questions,so all the totals are not in agreement. { { Newquay-Parents' Ages...Page 15 { Newquay Families........Page 16 { Men's Jobs in Newquay...Page 17 { Women's Jobs in Newquay.Page 18 { Housing in Newquay......Page 19 {
